WEBVTT

00:02.447 --> 00:05.771
Introducing...
Louie, Incorporated!

00:06.120 --> 00:08.555
It's a business.
It's a dream.

00:08.642 --> 00:10.491
It's a movement.

00:10.607 --> 00:13.111
Suits. Ties. Charts.

00:13.198 --> 00:14.952
Numbers. Yachts.

00:15.039 --> 00:17.280
Jet skis. You?

00:17.550 --> 00:21.100
Louie, Incorporated! It's a
dream, business, movement.

00:21.870 --> 00:23.849
- Did you
just do an Internet search

00:23.936 --> 00:25.330
for the word "business"?

00:25.417 --> 00:26.636
That's a trade secret.

00:26.723 --> 00:28.382
So is it...

00:28.525 --> 00:30.414
some kind of
lemonade stand or...?

00:30.501 --> 00:33.897
It's a dream of tomorrow
made manifest today.

00:35.511 --> 00:38.185
Okay, so there's some things
I haven't figured out yet.

00:38.272 --> 00:40.975
Like what your business
sells, does, and is.

00:41.062 --> 00:44.349
Sure, yeah, but... this
business is everything to me.

00:44.436 --> 00:47.333
I want to be a successful
businessman like you,

00:47.420 --> 00:49.491
'cause you're, like,
my idol and...

00:49.611 --> 00:51.671
possibly angel investor?

00:52.190 --> 00:54.555
You cannae just set out
to make money.

00:54.642 --> 00:57.725
You have to find a problem
and offer a solution.

00:57.812 --> 00:59.707
My problem is,
I need money.

00:59.794 --> 01:03.100
And if you would just give it to
me already, problem solutioned.

01:03.187 --> 01:06.538
Louie, Louie, Louie.
Look at your Uncle Donald.

01:06.644 --> 01:08.907
He saw there was a housing
shortage in Duckburg,

01:08.994 --> 01:11.055
so he's renting out the spare
room in his houseboat.

01:11.142 --> 01:12.439
Problem, solution.

01:12.526 --> 01:15.605
He's helping people, and...
Is he stealing my chandelier?

01:15.692 --> 01:17.034
Oi!

01:18.901 --> 01:21.642
But it takes money
to make money, right?

01:21.729 --> 01:25.132
I just need a tiny little bit,
and I'll get out of your hair.

01:25.362 --> 01:27.616
All right, lad.
How much do you need?

01:27.706 --> 01:29.651
2.5 billion, please.

01:31.000 --> 01:37.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

01:41.848 --> 01:43.254
Fancy!

01:44.568 --> 01:46.372
Waah! Earthquake!

01:46.459 --> 01:49.029
Batten down the hatches!

01:52.834 --> 01:54.470
Aw, phooey!

01:54.584 --> 01:56.207
O glorious day!

01:56.294 --> 01:59.225
The gods smile
upon our meeting. Ha, ha!

01:59.312 --> 02:01.192
Storkules?
You gotta go.

02:01.279 --> 02:03.265
My new tenant will
be here any minute.

02:03.352 --> 02:05.867
Me wonderest what blessed
soul be so fortunate

02:05.954 --> 02:09.068
as to share quarters with
the legendary Donald Duck, hmm?

02:09.155 --> 02:12.331
I don't know. Go,
before you scare him away!

02:12.418 --> 02:14.867
But wouldst that
even be possible

02:14.954 --> 02:17.185
if your new roommate
were incapable

02:17.272 --> 02:20.618
of feeling fear, hmm?

02:21.279 --> 02:22.278
Oh, no.

02:22.365 --> 02:25.765
If indeed he were the Defender
of Delphi, the Lion of Lindos...

02:25.852 --> 02:27.948
- Oh, no.
- For what if he

02:28.035 --> 02:30.462
be I, Storkules!

02:30.560 --> 02:32.431
Slumber party!

